# Large generated artifacts that aren't reproducible from git state alone:
# - Corpus JSONL is regeneratable from the labeler binary + ripgrep clone
# - Facts JSONL and per-commit diffs are regeneratable from the labeler's
#   `emit-facts` / `emit-diffs` subcommands over the corpus + ripgrep clone
# - Spot-check working-copy files (.bak, .PARKED) are local-only
corpus/*.jsonl
facts/*.facts.jsonl
facts/*.diffs/
spotcheck/*.bak
spotcheck/*.PARKED
work/

# Keep the directory itself tracked via .gitkeep
!.gitkeep
